OL,6, What's all this obsession with thinness
OL,7, about? No, not supermodels, technology.
OL,8, Wafer thin phones, tablets, laptops and
OL,9, such. I mention it because I remember  
OL,10, when I were a lad we had equipment in  
OL,11, school that could've probably survived 
OL,12, even the most careless of pupil - or   
OL,13, teacher, for that matter.              
OL,15, In an age where we seem to like giving 
OL,16, children iPads and whatnot to work on, 
OL,17, spare a thought for the old workhorses 
OL,18, of days gone by.                       
