OL,7, of the classroom audio toolkit, the    
OL,8, Coomber tape deck. No messing about,   
OL,9, it plays tapes and it's not going to   
OL,10, take any of your messing about. Solid  
OL,11, clunky buttons, quarter inch headphone 
OL,12, sockets, big twiddly knobs. Possibly   
OL,13, also a 2-pin DIN plug for a big speaker
OL,14, in the hall. While we're on the subject
OL,15, we might as well give a nod to the big 
