OL,7, a moment to consider whether what I'm  
OL,8, writing has a point.                   
OL,10, It doesn't really, other than to lament
OL,11, the loss of such classroom technology  
OL,12, icons, the likes of which could come   
OL,13, out the other end of a car crusher     
